 
<p>

Widespread use of disinfectant wipes <a href="https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2023/may/11/concern-over-increase-in-disinfectant-wipes-linked-to-health-problems">spread exposure to certain
    chemicals</a>, which could be harmful.
  Some researchers say the chemicals are linked to serious health problems, they
contribute to antimicrobial resistance, they pollute the environment
and they are not particularly effective.

 